{"tid":1180562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"舒寧咸畀料：簽一個人可令曼聯復甦","createTime":"2019-06-01T02:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T10:34:01.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc991020ddc3b9c6b351bcfd89f5b99cac6bff9b","tid":1180562,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"曼聯早前舉辦三冠王20周年紀念賽，一班名宿踢出魔性，對比依家嘅曼聯不禁令人心痛。踢完呢場紀念賽，舒寧咸有感而發，佢提議曼聯簽入李斯特城嘅哈利馬古尼，解決防線問題之後，曼聯才有復甦希望。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舒寧咸指出：「出色後防球員對一支球隊非常重要，例如曼城嘅高柏尼，又或者阿仙奴嘅阿當斯，我認為哈利馬古尼係其中一個，佢具備成為領袖嘅潛質，作用同里奧費迪南好類似。頂級球員，自然會懂得選擇加入頂級球隊。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哈利馬古尼嘅身價愈搶愈高，據報其轉會費高達7500萬鎊(約7.5億港元)，曼聯領隊蘇斯克查有2億鎊資金掃貨，舒寧咸就認為要喺防線位置花啲錢。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"0b456e8707c729edb1eb68e8a0e6c67104c6221d","tid":1180562,"uid":12034,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"屌 呢條老坑咁撚識波???"},{"pid":"b7d49743f7d1ed42f05ecca66477d6dfaa9b3389","tid":1180562,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b456e8707c729edb1eb68e8a0e6c67104c6221d","tid":1180562,"uid":12034,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"屌 呢條老坑咁撚識波???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599ec08f1a71d4f382292225be3108f41db21252","tid":1180562,"uid":143582,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"簽美斯"},{"pid":"5e55235351ee4fdf4921db07fdb11dfaa1c384ab","tid":1180562,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣連自己個仔都教唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29d903bf096cb2f079105ffac76f4d4da871a73","tid":1180562,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b456e8707c729edb1eb68e8a0e6c67104c6221d","tid":1180562,"uid":12034,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T02:44:04.000Z","ms